#: ..\..\create_vector_data\actions.rst:211
# c994fd50fb6d41f68a30ca21b593cc4e
msgid "Now you want QGIS to tell the browser to tell Google to search for the value of :kbd:`SGADMIN` for any feature that you could click on. Sounds complicated, but QGIS lets you do this easily."
msgstr ""

#: ..\..\create_vector_data\actions.rst:215
# 3e17e3863a094a7c9cddb4581455dcc3
msgid "Select the :guilabel:`SGADMIN` field."
